{"parse":{"title":"Equal Opportunities Commission (Hong Kong)","pageid":25801972,"revid":832056709,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"plainlinks metadata ambox ambox-content ambox-Unreferenced\" role=\"presentation\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mbox-image\"><div style=\"width:52px\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Question_book-new.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/99/Question_book-new.svg/50px-Question_book-new.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"39\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/99/Question_book-new.svg/75px-Question_book-new.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/99/Question_book-new.svg/100px-Question_book-new.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"512\" data-file-height=\"399\" /></a></div></td><td class=\"mbox-text\"><div class=\"mbox-text-span\">This article <b>does not <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Citing_sources\" title=\"Wikipedia:Citing sources\">cite</a> any <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Verifiability\" title=\"Wikipedia:Verifiability\">sources</a></b>.<span class=\"hide-when-compact\"> Please help <a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Equal_Opportunities_Commission_(Hong_Kong)&amp;action=edit\">improve this article</a> by <a href=\"/wiki/Help:Introduction_to_referencing_with_Wiki_Markup/1\" title=\"Help:Introduction to referencing with Wiki Markup/1\">adding citations to reliable sources</a>. Unsourced material may be challenged and <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Verifiability#Burden_of_evidence\" title=\"Wikipedia:Verifiability\">removed</a>.</span>  <small><i>(November 2016)</i></small><small class=\"hide-when-compact\"><i> (<a href=\"/wiki/Help:Maintenance_template_removal\" title=\"Help:Maintenance template removal\">Learn how and when to remove this template message</a>)</i></small></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n\n</p>\n<table class=\"infobox vcard\" style=\"width:22em\"><caption class=\"fn org\">Equal Opportunities Commission</caption><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<span class=\"nickname\">\u5e73\u7b49\u6a5f\u6703\u59d4\u54e1\u6703</span></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.6em;\">Abbreviation</th><td class=\"nickname\">\nEOC</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.6em;\">Formation</th><td class=\"note\">\n1996</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.6em;\">Type</th><td>\nStatutory Body</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.6em;\">Headquarters</th><td>\n16/F., 41 Heung Yip Road, <a href=\"/wiki/Wong_Chuk_Hang\" title=\"Wong Chuk Hang\">Wong Chuk Hang</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.6em;\">Location</th><td class=\"label\">\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><span class=\"flagicon\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5b/Flag_of_Hong_Kong.svg/23px-Flag_of_Hong_Kong.svg.png\" width=\"23\" height=\"15\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5b/Flag_of_Hong_Kong.svg/35px-Flag_of_Hong_Kong.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5b/Flag_of_Hong_Kong.svg/45px-Flag_of_Hong_Kong.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"900\" data-file-height=\"600\" />&#160;</span><a href=\"/wiki/Hong_Kong\" title=\"Hong Kong\">Hong Kong</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.6em;\"><div style=\"padding:0.1em 0;line-height:1.2em;\">Chairperson</div></th><td>\nAlfred CHAN Cheung-ming</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.6em;\"><div style=\"padding:0.1em 0;line-height:1.2em;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Board_of_directors\" title=\"Board of directors\"><span class=\"wrap\">Board&#160;of directors</span></a></div></th><td>\n<p>Cecilia CHAN Lai-wan<br /> \nAndy CHIU Man-chung<br /> \nSusanne CHOI Yuk-ping<br /> \nHolden CHOW Ho-ding<br /> \nMohan DATWANI<br /> \nMaisy HO Chiu-ha<br /> \nMaggie KOONG May-kay<br /> \nElizabeth LAW<br /> \nTrisha LEAHY<br /> \nJoseph LEE Kok-long<br /> \nJuan LEUNG Chung-yan<br /> \nShirley Marie Therese LOO<br /> \nHenry SHIE Wai-hung<br /> \nRizwan ULLAH<br /> \n</p>\nYU Chui-yee</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.6em;\"><div style=\"padding:0.1em 0;line-height:1.2em;\">Budget <span style=\"font-weight:normal;\">(2017)</span> </div></th><td>\nHK$112,510,994</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.6em;\">Expenses <span style=\"font-weight:normal;\">(2017)</span></th><td>\nHK$115,380,579</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"width:22em\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size: 125%; background-color: #b0c4de;\">\nEqual Opportunities Commission</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Traditional_Chinese_characters\" title=\"Traditional Chinese characters\">Traditional&#160;Chinese</a></th><td>\n<span style=\"font-size: 1rem\"><span lang=\"zh-Hant\" title=\"Chinese language text\">\u5e73\u7b49\u6a5f\u6703\u59d4\u54e1\u6703</span></span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table class=\"collapsible collapsed\" style=\"padding:0;border:none;margin:-3px;width:auto;min-width:100%;font-size:100%;clear:none;float:none;background-color:transparent\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-size: 100%; text-align: left; background-color: #f9ffbc;\">Transcriptions</th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color: #dcffc9;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Cantonese\" title=\"Cantonese\">Yue: Cantonese</a></th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Yale_romanization_of_Cantonese\" title=\"Yale romanization of Cantonese\">Yale Romanization</a></th><td>\nP\u00echng d\u00e1ng g\u0113i wuih w\u00e1i y\u00f9hn wuih</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Jyutping\" title=\"Jyutping\">Jyutping</a></th><td>\nPing<sup>4</sup> dang<sup>2</sup> gei<sup>1</sup> wui<sup>6</sup> wai<sup>2</sup> jyun<sup>4</sup> wui<sup>6*2</sup></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr style=\"display:none\"><td colspan=\"2\">\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Equal Opportunities Commission</b> (EOC) is a government-funded statutory body in <a href=\"/wiki/Hong_Kong\" title=\"Hong Kong\">Hong Kong</a>, established in 1996, responsible for implementing the various anti-discrimination ordinances in Hong Kong. The Commission is committed to promoting <a href=\"/wiki/Diversity_(politics)\" title=\"Diversity (politics)\">diversity</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Social_equality\" title=\"Social equality\">equality</a>, fostering an inclusive society in which all individuals are treated with <a href=\"/wiki/Respect\" title=\"Respect\">respect</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Dignity\" title=\"Dignity\">dignity</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Mission\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Mission</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#List_of_Chairpersons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">List of Chairpersons</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Controversies\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Controversies</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#The_&#39;Michael_Wong_Kin-chow_incident&#39;\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">The 'Michael Wong Kin-chow incident'</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Statements_by_Alfred_Chen\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Statements by Alfred Chen</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mission\">Mission</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Equal_Opportunities_Commission_(Hong_Kong)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Mission\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Commission's mission is to eliminate <a href=\"/wiki/Discrimination\" title=\"Discrimination\">discrimination</a>, to promote <a href=\"/wiki/Equal_opportunity\" title=\"Equal opportunity\">equal opportunities</a>, and to help people understand their rights and obligations under Hong Kong's anti-discrimination <a href=\"/wiki/Legislation\" title=\"Legislation\">legislation</a> and provide <a href=\"/wiki/Redress\" title=\"Redress\">redress</a> for discrimination. At present, the anti-discrimination ordinances in Hong Kong are:\n</p>\n<ul><li>the <a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Sex_Discrimination_Ordinance&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Sex Discrimination Ordinance (page does not exist)\">Sex Discrimination Ordinance</a></li>\n<li>the <a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Disability_Discrimination_Ordinance&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Disability Discrimination Ordinance (page does not exist)\">Disability Discrimination Ordinance</a></li>\n<li>the <a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Family_Status_Discrimination_Ordinance&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Family Status Discrimination Ordinance (page does not exist)\">Family Status Discrimination Ordinance</a></li>\n<li>the <a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Race_Discrimination_Ordinance&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Race Discrimination Ordinance (page does not exist)\">Race Discrimination Ordinance</a></li></ul>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Tram,_Wan_Chai,_Hong_Kong.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/58/Tram%2C_Wan_Chai%2C_Hong_Kong.jpg/300px-Tram%2C_Wan_Chai%2C_Hong_Kong.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/58/Tram%2C_Wan_Chai%2C_Hong_Kong.jpg/450px-Tram%2C_Wan_Chai%2C_Hong_Kong.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/58/Tram%2C_Wan_Chai%2C_Hong_Kong.jpg/600px-Tram%2C_Wan_Chai%2C_Hong_Kong.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"2700\" data-file-height=\"1800\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Tram,_Wan_Chai,_Hong_Kong.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Tram body ads of the EOC, HK</div></div></div>\n<p>The main functions of the EOC are to: investigate complaints and issues related to its mandate to uphold the anti-discrimination ordinances and act as an intermediary between affected parties, to issues codes of practice and guidelines for implementing the ordinances, to propose legislative amendments relevant to the elimination of discrimination, and to provide educational services to promote awareness of the ordinances.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Equal_Opportunities_Commission_(Hong_Kong)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:222px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Hong_Kong_LAM_Woon-kwong_as_Chairperson_of_the_Equal_Opportunities_Commission.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fb/Hong_Kong_LAM_Woon-kwong_as_Chairperson_of_the_Equal_Opportunities_Commission.JPG/220px-Hong_Kong_LAM_Woon-kwong_as_Chairperson_of_the_Equal_Opportunities_Commission.JPG\" width=\"220\" height=\"165\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fb/Hong_Kong_LAM_Woon-kwong_as_Chairperson_of_the_Equal_Opportunities_Commission.JPG/330px-Hong_Kong_LAM_Woon-kwong_as_Chairperson_of_the_Equal_Opportunities_Commission.JPG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fb/Hong_Kong_LAM_Woon-kwong_as_Chairperson_of_the_Equal_Opportunities_Commission.JPG/440px-Hong_Kong_LAM_Woon-kwong_as_Chairperson_of_the_Equal_Opportunities_Commission.JPG 2x\" data-file-width=\"2592\" data-file-height=\"1944\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Hong_Kong_LAM_Woon-kwong_as_Chairperson_of_the_Equal_Opportunities_Commission.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Hong Kong LAM Woon-kwong as Chairperson of the Equal Opportunities Commission</div></div></div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"List_of_Chairpersons\">List of Chairpersons</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Equal_Opportunities_Commission_(Hong_Kong)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: List of Chairpersons\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Name</th>\n<th>Photo</th>\n<th>Tenure</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Anna_Wu\" title=\"Anna Wu\">Anna WU</a><br />\u80e1\u7d05\u7389\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:Anna_Wu_Hung-yuk.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Anna Wu Hung-yuk.JPG\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4e/Anna_Wu_Hung-yuk.JPG/100px-Anna_Wu_Hung-yuk.JPG\" width=\"100\" height=\"131\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4e/Anna_Wu_Hung-yuk.JPG/150px-Anna_Wu_Hung-yuk.JPG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4e/Anna_Wu_Hung-yuk.JPG/200px-Anna_Wu_Hung-yuk.JPG 2x\" data-file-width=\"233\" data-file-height=\"305\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td>1 August 1999 - 31 July 2003\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Michael WONG Kin-chow<br />\u738b\u898b\u79cb\n</th>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>1 August 2003 - 6 November 2003\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Patricia CHU YEUNG Pak-yu<br />\u6731\u694a\u73c0\u745c\n</th>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>15 December 2003 - 15 December 2004\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Raymond TANG Yee-Bong<br />\u9127\u723e\u90a6\n</th>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>12 January 2005 \u2013 28 February 2010\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Lam_Woon-kwong\" title=\"Lam Woon-kwong\">LAM Woon-kwong</a><br />\u6797\u7165\u5149\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:Lam_Woon-kwong.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Lam Woon-kwong.JPG\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Lam_Woon-kwong.JPG/100px-Lam_Woon-kwong.JPG\" width=\"100\" height=\"133\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Lam_Woon-kwong.JPG/150px-Lam_Woon-kwong.JPG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Lam_Woon-kwong.JPG/200px-Lam_Woon-kwong.JPG 2x\" data-file-width=\"876\" data-file-height=\"1168\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td>1 February 2010 \u2013 31 March 2013\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/York_Chow\" title=\"York Chow\">Dr. York CHOW Yat-Ngok</a><br />\u5468\u4e00\u5dbd\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:York_Chow_Yat-ngok.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"York Chow Yat-ngok.jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/57/York_Chow_Yat-ngok.jpg/100px-York_Chow_Yat-ngok.jpg\" width=\"100\" height=\"152\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/57/York_Chow_Yat-ngok.jpg/150px-York_Chow_Yat-ngok.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/57/York_Chow_Yat-ngok.jpg/200px-York_Chow_Yat-ngok.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"395\" data-file-height=\"602\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td>1 April 2013 \u2013 31 March 2016\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Prof. Alfred CHAN Cheung-ming<br />\u9673\u7ae0\u660e\n</th>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>11 April 2016 \u2013\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Controversies\">Controversies</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Equal_Opportunities_Commission_(Hong_Kong)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Controversies\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span id=\"The_.27Michael_Wong_Kin-chow_incident.27\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_'Michael_Wong_Kin-chow_incident'\">The 'Michael Wong Kin-chow incident'</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Equal_Opportunities_Commission_(Hong_Kong)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: The &#039;Michael Wong Kin-chow incident&#039;\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>In 2003, Michael Wong Kin-chow was removed as the Chairman of the EOC after an investivation by the <a href=\"/wiki/Independent_Commission_Against_Corruption_(Hong_Kong)\" title=\"Independent Commission Against Corruption (Hong Kong)\">Independent Commission Against Corruption</a> (ICAC) revealed that Mr Wong had deliberately made improper applications to the HKSAR government for reimbursement of several first-class flights between 1998 and 2001, valued at HK$171,666.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> It was also reported that Mr Wong had continued to draw his pension as a former High Court judge while he was employed at the EOC. The ICAC's report was submitted to the <a href=\"/wiki/Director_of_Public_Prosecutions\" title=\"Director of Public Prosecutions\">Director of Public Prosecutions</a> (DPP) in November 2005 who ultimately decided not to proceed with prosecution.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Statements_by_Alfred_Chen\">Statements by Alfred Chen</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Equal_Opportunities_Commission_(Hong_Kong)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Statements by Alfred Chen\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>On 1 June 2016, a concern was raised by some legislators that the newly appointed Chairperson, Prof Alfred Chen, had expressed views which suggested he was not suitably aware of the key issues necessary to execute his duties as head of the EOC. These included a dismissal of the need to address the lack of any anti-discrimination ordinance to protect sexual minorities, confusion of concepts such as gender identity and sexual orientation, and declaring that the EOC should echo the views of the government.<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Equal_Opportunities_Commission_(Hong_Kong)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Human_rights_in_Hong_Kong\" title=\"Human rights in Hong Kong\">Human rights in Hong Kong</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/LGBT_rights_in_Hong_Kong\" title=\"LGBT rights in Hong Kong\">LGBT rights in Hong Kong</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Equal_Opportunities_Commission_(Hong_Kong)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Information Services Department <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.gov.hk/en/about/abouthk/factsheets/docs/eoc.pdf\">\" The Equal Opportunities Commission\"</a>, <i>Hong Kong: The Facts</i>, Hong Kong, June 2015. Retrieved on 6 December 2017.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Community Legal Information Centre <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.clic.org.hk/en/topics/antiDiscrimination/introduction_to_hk_anti_discrimination/q2.shtml\">\"What are the functions and duties of the Equal Opportunities Commission (EOC)?\"</a>, <i><a href=\"/wiki/University_of_Hong_Kong\" title=\"University of Hong Kong\">University of Hong Kong</a></i>, Hong Kong, 2017, Accessed on 6 December 2017</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The Government 